text: Axel Alarik Pehrsson-Bramstorp, born Axel Alarik Pehrsson, 19 August 1883, dead 19 February 1954, was a Swedish politician. He served as the Prime Minister of Sweden for a few months during mid 1936. == References == Category:1883 births Category:1954 deaths Category:Government ministers of Sweden Category:Prime ministers of Sweden
title: Axel Pehrsson-Bramstorp
